=Description=

The Occupied Wall Street Journal collaborated with Occuprint to produce a poster folio as their fourth issue. We've printed 20,000 copies of this issue, to be distributed throughout our movement. If you get your hands on one, please use it. Hang up posters, help us make this movement more visible in physical spaces, not just virtual ones. 


